WEBVTT

00:12.050 --> 00:15.370
[1995]

00:13.000 --> 00:14.400
Come on, guys, over here!

00:14.830 --> 00:16.360
The rain's letting up a bit!

00:16.520 --> 00:17.580
Let's hurry and move

00:17.580 --> 00:21.690
[Jiang Hansheng (Child)]

00:17.780 --> 00:19.260
before it gets heavy again.

00:19.260 --> 00:19.780
Come on.

00:20.060 --> 00:20.660
Turn left.

00:21.240 --> 00:22.100
Be careful!

00:22.350 --> 00:23.870
Turn right!

00:24.480 --> 00:25.670
Let me have a turn!

00:25.760 --> 00:27.620
The road is slippery! Be careful!

00:27.960 --> 00:29.020
Look, everyone,

00:29.040 --> 00:30.300
we have new neighbors!

00:31.840 --> 00:32.170
Here!

00:32.180 --> 00:32.900
Jin, run!

00:33.200 --> 00:33.960
Let's go!

00:35.080 --> 00:35.890
It's my turn!

00:35.920 --> 00:37.580
Jiang Cheng, that's not fair!

00:38.010 --> 00:39.670
What's your name, little one?

00:39.960 --> 00:41.110
My name is Zhou Jin.

00:42.790 --> 00:43.400
Hansheng.

00:44.270 --> 00:46.270
Look how fast that little girl runs.

00:46.920 --> 00:48.590
Her legs are spinning like a windmill.

00:48.590 --> 00:49.350
Not fair!

00:49.520 --> 00:50.470
Not fair!

00:50.470 --> 00:51.860
It's okay, Yan Bin! I'll get it for you!

00:51.860 --> 00:53.390
Come and take it if you dare!

00:55.660 --> 00:56.260
Hansheng,

00:57.070 --> 00:58.360
look how nice it is here.

00:58.030 --> 01:02.130
[Jiang Bozhi, Jiang Hansheng's Father]

00:58.840 --> 00:59.770
Don't you think?

00:59.840 --> 01:00.610
From now on,

01:00.630 --> 01:02.430
you can play with them every day.

01:03.100 --> 01:05.480
Don't just stay cooped up at home
reading books all the time,

01:05.480 --> 01:06.250
okay?

01:11.470 --> 01:12.460
Come on! Come on, guys!

01:12.460 --> 01:13.110
This way!

01:15.539 --> 01:16.570
It's spinning!

01:17.890 --> 01:22.000
[Zhou Jin (Child)]

02:53.860 --> 02:59.829
[Sunsets Secrets Regrets]

03:00.190 --> 03:02.540
[Episode 2]

03:23.440 --> 03:25.370
The security camera is over there.

03:28.380 --> 03:29.600
On the night of the murder,

03:29.600 --> 03:30.620
when the victim took the taxi,

03:30.620 --> 03:32.120
she seemed completely normal.

03:32.120 --> 03:33.160
And that late at night,

03:33.160 --> 03:35.220
going to the suburbs to meet someone—

03:35.230 --> 03:36.950
that person was almost certainly
an acquaintance of hers.

03:36.950 --> 03:38.230
By investigating her social connections,

03:38.230 --> 03:40.000
we'll likely find that person.

03:41.600 --> 03:42.630
She probably had

03:42.880 --> 03:44.780
a more complex social circle than most.

03:44.780 --> 03:45.710
That's strange.

03:46.250 --> 03:47.670
During the time she was missing,

03:47.670 --> 03:49.270
no one reported her absence.

03:50.230 --> 03:51.630
That can only mean the victim

03:51.630 --> 03:52.790
had no relatives or friends

03:52.790 --> 03:53.760
in Haizhou City.

03:54.200 --> 03:55.600
Even when she disappeared,

03:55.600 --> 03:56.440
nobody cared.

03:57.480 --> 03:58.320
No job,

03:58.350 --> 03:59.040
no family.

03:59.630 --> 04:01.160
For such a glamorous woman,

04:01.480 --> 04:03.140
what was her source of income?

04:05.000 --> 04:05.670
Hello.

04:07.950 --> 04:08.390
Hello.

04:08.440 --> 04:12.170
We're from the Criminal Investigation Brigade,
Nancheng Branch.

04:12.440 --> 04:13.200
Do you recognize

04:13.200 --> 04:13.930
this person?

04:14.670 --> 04:15.350
She's dead.

04:16.200 --> 04:17.360
We need you to

04:17.540 --> 04:19.589
truthfully provide all information
about her.

04:19.589 --> 04:20.120
I didn't know her.

04:20.120 --> 04:21.180
I'd never seen her.

04:21.339 --> 04:22.470
You didn't know her?

04:23.120 --> 04:24.270
Take your staff ID

04:24.840 --> 04:25.770
and come with me.

04:35.370 --> 04:36.770
Customizable services.

04:37.030 --> 04:38.030
Is it legitimate?

04:38.320 --> 04:39.320
It's legitimate.

04:47.400 --> 04:49.330
Since she chose this type of hotel,

04:49.600 --> 04:50.770
she probably didn't have

04:50.770 --> 04:51.970
money to spare.

04:52.890 --> 04:53.890
There was

04:54.190 --> 04:55.430
a subtle sexual undertone

04:55.430 --> 04:56.630
in her body language.

04:57.150 --> 04:58.750
She was waiting for her taxi,

04:58.800 --> 05:00.390
but whenever men passed by,

05:00.640 --> 05:02.830
she would instinctively display herself.

05:02.830 --> 05:04.630
Probably a professional habit.

05:04.800 --> 05:06.000
You mean

05:06.630 --> 05:08.000
she was a prostitute?

05:14.190 --> 05:15.650
Quite well-stocked here.

05:16.990 --> 05:17.500
Hello.

05:18.320 --> 05:19.720
Hello, officers. I'm...

05:19.880 --> 05:21.140
the room manager here.

05:21.150 --> 05:22.320
How can I help you?

05:22.630 --> 05:25.290
I'll fully cooperate
with your investigation.

05:26.860 --> 05:27.590
These items?

05:27.670 --> 05:29.070
They're just promotional items.

05:29.070 --> 05:29.950
Some guests

05:29.950 --> 05:31.080
have certain needs,

05:31.090 --> 05:31.850
so they buy these things here—

05:31.850 --> 05:34.050
it saves them a trip to the supermarket.

05:36.800 --> 05:38.060
Skip the formalities.

05:39.070 --> 05:41.120
Do you typically procure prostitutes

05:41.120 --> 05:43.450
or just provide venues for prostitution?

05:44.350 --> 05:45.950
You must be joking, officer.

05:52.120 --> 05:53.150
Are you her boss

05:53.950 --> 05:54.810
or her partner?

05:56.560 --> 05:57.590
I don't know her.

05:58.020 --> 05:58.659
I don't.

06:01.130 --> 06:02.930
No one can keep secrets forever.

06:03.070 --> 06:04.400
When people won't talk,

06:04.860 --> 06:07.060
their fingers can still tell the story.

06:07.800 --> 06:08.630
So can toes.

06:09.860 --> 06:11.660
You really have a sense of humor.

06:12.100 --> 06:13.120
Wasting our time

06:13.150 --> 06:14.350
won't do you any good.

06:14.960 --> 06:16.560
The girl in the photo is dead.

06:17.290 --> 06:18.220
This is serious.

06:18.820 --> 06:20.280
I'll ask you one last time:

06:20.390 --> 06:21.660
do you know her or not?

06:24.390 --> 06:25.250
Won't talk, eh?

06:25.630 --> 06:27.660
Let's continue
this conversation elsewhere.

06:27.660 --> 06:28.340
Meng Ling.

06:28.470 --> 06:29.690
Her name was Meng Ling.

06:29.690 --> 06:30.890
I knew her, I knew her.

06:33.800 --> 06:35.000
That night, Meng Ling

06:35.070 --> 06:35.680
was supposed to

06:35.680 --> 06:37.470
meet a pimp named Lai San.

06:38.200 --> 06:40.030
Meng Ling must have had

06:40.030 --> 06:41.159
some dirt on Lai San,

06:41.400 --> 06:42.140
using it to threaten him,

06:42.140 --> 06:44.159
and that's what got her into trouble.

06:44.159 --> 06:45.880
We have already issued a statement.

06:45.880 --> 06:46.880
They all knew her.

06:47.070 --> 06:48.400
Why did no one report it?

06:48.530 --> 06:50.240
Because on the 23rd, Meng Ling

06:50.240 --> 06:51.370
told the hotel staff

06:51.510 --> 06:52.710
that she was going back to her hometown

06:52.710 --> 06:54.040
and would never return.

06:54.300 --> 06:55.440
She must have been really confident

06:55.440 --> 06:56.470
that she could settle things

06:56.470 --> 06:57.680
with Lai San

06:57.680 --> 06:58.880
and return to her hometown smoothly.

06:58.880 --> 07:00.400
So even when something happened to her,

07:00.400 --> 07:03.150
the hotel staff just assumed
she went back to her hometown.

07:03.150 --> 07:04.680
What's Lai San's real name?

07:05.030 --> 07:06.030
We don't know yet.

07:06.560 --> 07:08.420
We only know that's his nickname.

07:08.830 --> 07:10.360
But he told the hotel staff

07:10.680 --> 07:12.940
that his cousin was about to
open a new bar

07:13.200 --> 07:15.460
and that he would manage it in the future.

07:15.570 --> 07:17.170
It's opening tonight at 8 PM.

07:17.290 --> 07:18.290
The bar's name is

07:18.600 --> 07:21.090
[Phoenix Fire Bar]

07:19.480 --> 07:20.280
Phoenix Fire.

07:28.440 --> 07:30.570
Meng Ling was killed several days ago.

07:30.950 --> 07:32.270
We can't rule out the possibility

07:32.270 --> 07:34.320
that Lai San has already fled
to avoid punishment.

07:34.320 --> 07:34.880
So

07:34.950 --> 07:36.150
tonight's operation

07:36.560 --> 07:38.030
is not just to find Lai San

07:38.390 --> 07:39.320
but also to find

07:39.800 --> 07:40.630
his cousin,

07:40.950 --> 07:41.470
He Wu.

07:43.950 --> 07:44.680
Zhou Jin.

07:45.470 --> 07:47.000
Go check the private rooms.

07:48.100 --> 07:48.780
Roger that.

07:49.570 --> 07:51.030
He Wu's business dealings

07:51.030 --> 07:52.320
are mostly illegal.

07:52.590 --> 07:54.240
We have been watching him for a long time,

07:54.240 --> 07:56.510
but we haven't found solid evidence yet.

07:57.030 --> 07:58.000
If Meng Ling

07:58.030 --> 07:59.760
was indeed killed by Lai San,

08:00.060 --> 08:00.570
then

08:00.790 --> 08:02.030
we have to suspect

08:02.140 --> 08:03.410
that He Wu

08:04.030 --> 08:04.680
knew about

08:05.120 --> 08:06.390
the gun.

08:09.620 --> 08:10.970
Please stop hitting me!

08:11.830 --> 08:13.160
I can't take it anymore!

08:13.680 --> 08:14.950
I'll never do it again!

08:15.120 --> 08:15.710
Cheng!

08:16.360 --> 08:17.620
Just chop off one of his hands.

08:17.620 --> 08:19.200
Let's see if he dares to do it again!

08:19.200 --> 08:20.440
Don't chop off my hand.

08:20.440 --> 08:21.080
Cheng,

08:21.380 --> 08:23.170
I really know I was wrong.

08:23.200 --> 08:24.360
Please stop hitting me!

08:24.360 --> 08:25.480
I'm begging you!

08:25.870 --> 08:27.750
We keep you around to work for us,

08:27.910 --> 08:29.310
and you, little bastard,

08:29.590 --> 08:31.790
dare to steal from us to sell on your own?

08:38.350 --> 08:39.590
I needed money!

08:39.590 --> 08:40.919
My mother is sick!

08:41.330 --> 08:43.000
I really needed the money!

08:43.490 --> 08:44.830
Cheng, I promise

08:45.350 --> 08:46.920
I'll work like a dog

08:46.920 --> 08:48.400
and pay you back every cent!

08:48.400 --> 08:49.730
Please stop hitting me!

08:51.160 --> 08:52.000
Help me!

08:52.030 --> 08:53.070
Help!

08:53.090 --> 08:55.050
Someone, please help me!

08:56.760 --> 08:58.220
They're beating him so badly.

08:58.220 --> 08:59.410
What should we do, sis?

08:59.410 --> 09:00.350
Let's go, quickly.

09:00.350 --> 09:00.830
Leave it alone.

09:00.830 --> 09:01.710
It's none of our business.

09:01.710 --> 09:03.280
Don't get yourself in trouble.

09:03.280 --> 09:04.610
I can't take it anymore!

09:10.590 --> 09:11.830
Stop hitting me!

09:11.850 --> 09:14.330
I needed money! My mother is sick!

09:14.870 --> 09:16.840
I really needed the money!

09:18.460 --> 09:19.060
Chief Tan,

09:19.320 --> 09:22.000
it sounds like people are fighting
in the storage room.

09:22.000 --> 09:22.840
Don't worry.

09:23.200 --> 09:24.130
Leave it for now.

09:24.410 --> 09:25.980
I'll send Wu to check it out.

09:26.610 --> 09:27.160
Roger.

09:29.790 --> 09:31.390
Help!

09:32.440 --> 09:34.990
Is anyone there to help me?

09:36.510 --> 09:39.320
Is anyone there to help me?

09:41.830 --> 09:42.440
Continue!

09:42.550 --> 09:43.260
Stop!

09:44.280 --> 09:45.340
What are you doing?

09:45.660 --> 09:46.320
Having fun.

09:47.280 --> 09:47.940
Having fun?

09:54.190 --> 09:54.920
Are you okay?

09:55.520 --> 09:56.760
Do you need me to call the police?

09:56.760 --> 09:58.760
Where did this nosy woman come from?

09:59.390 --> 10:00.720
Mind your own business.

10:01.190 --> 10:01.720
Get lost!

10:03.310 --> 10:05.950
You should treat a lady
with basic respect.

10:07.670 --> 10:10.940
[Jiang Cheng,
Vice President of Hengyun Logistics]

10:13.430 --> 10:15.360
What a beautiful lady.

10:25.030 --> 10:25.680
Bleach,

10:26.400 --> 10:27.520
you're lucky today.

10:27.520 --> 10:28.920
You've met a good person.

10:29.710 --> 10:31.770
Since this pretty lady is so curious,

10:31.980 --> 10:34.440
you'd better answer her question properly.

10:34.990 --> 10:35.520
I...

10:35.830 --> 10:37.590
don't need you to call the police.

10:37.590 --> 10:38.590
Did you hear that?

10:39.440 --> 10:40.950
Wanna have some fun

10:42.040 --> 10:42.880
with us?

10:44.920 --> 10:45.470
Get lost.

10:46.120 --> 10:47.640
She's quite feisty.

10:50.280 --> 10:50.830
Bleach,

10:51.070 --> 10:52.530
I'll give you two options:

10:52.640 --> 10:53.110
one,

10:53.690 --> 10:54.340
you leave,

10:55.200 --> 10:56.660
and this young lady stays.

10:56.710 --> 10:57.200
Two,

10:57.710 --> 10:58.970
the young lady leaves,

10:58.990 --> 10:59.800
and you stay.

11:00.560 --> 11:01.180
Choice!

11:08.790 --> 11:11.440
You brought this on yourself by meddling.

11:11.610 --> 11:13.940
You brought this on yourself by meddling.

11:18.990 --> 11:19.750
Miss,

11:20.330 --> 11:21.280
look at you,

11:21.670 --> 11:23.270
standing up for such a loser.

11:23.280 --> 11:24.080
Is it worth it?

11:27.770 --> 11:28.950
This chick's got some fire.

11:28.950 --> 11:29.480
Get lost!

11:30.950 --> 11:31.880
Get out of my way.

11:38.640 --> 11:39.770
Out on duty, are you?

11:41.110 --> 11:42.640
Who are you investigating?

11:43.910 --> 11:46.170
I know police tactics better than you do.

11:46.280 --> 11:47.320
Investigate all you want,

11:47.320 --> 11:49.980
but why stick your nose
where it doesn't belong?

11:50.320 --> 11:51.320
It's been 2 years.

11:52.130 --> 11:53.260
You're still alive.

11:54.240 --> 11:55.770
Wishing me dead that badly?

11:56.970 --> 11:58.630
I've missed you all this time.

11:58.950 --> 11:59.950
If I'm going to die,

11:59.950 --> 12:01.480
I'd rather die on top of you.

12:03.980 --> 12:04.640
Let go of me.

12:05.680 --> 12:06.320
Jin.

12:06.610 --> 12:08.040
You've really lost your touch.

12:08.040 --> 12:10.160
Don't ever tell people I trained you.

12:10.800 --> 12:11.640
Let go of me!

12:11.680 --> 12:12.520
What a temper.

12:12.720 --> 12:14.470
I was just messing with you,
and you're actually getting mad?

12:14.470 --> 12:15.130
Don't move!

12:16.680 --> 12:18.080
Let me take a closer look.

12:38.710 --> 12:40.310
You've really changed a lot.

12:41.990 --> 12:43.720
Why did you grow your hair long?

12:43.830 --> 12:45.490
Short hair suited you better.

12:45.520 --> 12:47.450
You're the one who's changed a lot.

12:47.960 --> 12:49.560
Jiang Cheng is already dead.

12:50.640 --> 12:51.400
Who are you?

12:58.280 --> 12:59.940
You're being so harsh with me.

13:03.750 --> 13:04.590
Don't forget.

13:05.580 --> 13:08.510
I'm probably the only one
who busted my own boyfriend

13:08.750 --> 13:11.040
during an anti-prostitution crackdown.

13:11.040 --> 13:13.820
[2012]

13:51.710 --> 13:54.110
If I catch any more evidence
of your crimes,

13:55.120 --> 13:56.850
I definitely won't let you off.

13:59.410 --> 14:00.470
-Jin...
-Get lost!

14:52.230 --> 14:53.890
We might have found the 3,000.

15:00.780 --> 15:01.870
Lai San

15:01.870 --> 15:04.470
has a very distinctive tattoo
on his right arm.

15:22.210 --> 15:24.140
I left the 3,000 at the bar counter.

15:24.870 --> 15:25.600
Bar counter!

15:25.750 --> 15:26.230
Move in!

15:45.610 --> 15:46.880
He's leaving, he's leaving.

15:46.880 --> 15:47.960
Zhou Jin, Zhou Jin,

15:47.990 --> 15:48.950
don't rush.

15:49.160 --> 15:50.420
You're still injured!

15:50.440 --> 15:51.970
Wait for the tactical team!

16:07.390 --> 16:08.250
Tactical team,

16:08.320 --> 16:09.550
surround the entire alley.

16:09.550 --> 16:10.980
Block both ends.

16:19.740 --> 16:21.270
There really are cops here.

16:23.790 --> 16:24.710
Are you Lai San?

16:25.920 --> 16:27.180
It's none of your business.

16:27.180 --> 16:28.240
Who are you anyway?

16:28.600 --> 16:30.360
Do you know whose turf this is?

16:30.630 --> 16:32.240
My cousin's bar just opened today,

16:32.240 --> 16:33.200
and you come to cause trouble?

16:33.200 --> 16:34.580
You did this on purpose, didn't you?

16:34.580 --> 16:35.220
Get her!

17:22.599 --> 17:23.270
Don't move!

17:23.359 --> 17:24.010
Freeze!

17:24.319 --> 17:24.910
Freeze!

17:25.390 --> 17:26.050
Don't move!

17:26.460 --> 17:26.970
Get down!

17:26.970 --> 17:27.569
Come down!

17:28.790 --> 17:29.720
Are you alright?

17:30.080 --> 17:30.540
I'm fine.

17:30.540 --> 17:31.200
Don't move!

17:33.670 --> 17:34.280
Cuff him!

17:53.450 --> 17:54.380
Why are you here?

17:56.080 --> 17:57.410
Class was rescheduled.

17:57.740 --> 17:58.470
Are you okay?

17:58.780 --> 17:59.450
I'm fine.

18:01.220 --> 18:01.790
Zhou Jin!

18:03.360 --> 18:05.600
Have you forgotten
your ribs are still injured?

18:05.600 --> 18:07.470
Didn't I tell you not to go in?

18:07.680 --> 18:08.870
I told you to wait for the tactical team.

18:08.870 --> 18:09.960
I told you!

18:10.160 --> 18:11.010
Why were you showing off?

18:11.010 --> 18:12.320
If I didn't chase him,
he would've escaped.

18:12.320 --> 18:13.380
Where could he run?

18:13.750 --> 18:14.920
We had him surrounded.

18:14.920 --> 18:15.960
Where could he possibly go?

18:15.960 --> 18:17.420
What, did he sprout wings?

18:18.600 --> 18:19.200
Chief Tan,

18:19.710 --> 18:21.750
-Zhou Jin did it for...
-Professor Jiang.

18:21.750 --> 18:23.030
I'm disciplining my subordinate.

18:23.030 --> 18:24.030
Please excuse us.

18:25.210 --> 18:25.610
Right,

18:26.240 --> 18:26.990
get in the car,

18:26.990 --> 18:29.320
and get that arm wound treated right away.

18:41.300 --> 18:43.700
Stop thinking you're such a great fighter.

18:44.340 --> 18:46.120
Did you follow my instructions?

18:46.120 --> 18:47.230
Did I give orders?

18:48.140 --> 18:49.940
You got lucky this time.

18:50.230 --> 18:51.430
What about next time?

18:52.050 --> 18:52.980
I'm telling you,

18:53.020 --> 18:54.480
if something happens to you,

18:54.480 --> 18:56.540
at least you'd die in the line of duty!

18:57.280 --> 18:58.950
But what if innocent bystanders
get involved and end up hurt?

18:58.950 --> 19:01.280
That would be a needless tragedy for them!

19:01.340 --> 19:02.740
You're a police officer.

19:03.390 --> 19:05.190
Who is supposed to protect whom?

19:07.170 --> 19:09.050
Go back and write a self-criticism report!

19:09.050 --> 19:09.640
Yes, sir.

19:11.720 --> 19:12.580
What about him?

19:16.710 --> 19:17.710
I know, I know.

19:18.550 --> 19:19.470
Write down the entire process

19:19.470 --> 19:20.840
in complete detail.

19:22.020 --> 19:24.400
Including the part where you took off
your earpiece and acted on your own.

19:24.400 --> 19:24.920
Also,

19:25.470 --> 19:27.160
when you go undercover in the future,

19:27.160 --> 19:28.300
don't wear just anything.

19:28.300 --> 19:29.960
What on earth are you wearing?

19:31.230 --> 19:31.960
Are you done?

19:31.990 --> 19:32.880
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

19:32.880 --> 19:33.550
Take them away!

19:33.550 --> 19:34.750
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

19:35.670 --> 19:36.200
Move!

19:37.950 --> 19:38.400
Move!

19:38.980 --> 19:39.980
Behave yourself!

19:46.430 --> 19:48.120
I'll kill you when I get out.

19:48.140 --> 19:48.390
Move!

19:48.390 --> 19:49.120
Keep moving!

19:54.040 --> 19:55.240
What did you just say?

19:55.290 --> 19:56.050
I said,

19:56.720 --> 19:58.240
I'll finish her.

20:00.080 --> 20:00.670
Professor Jiang!

20:00.670 --> 20:00.990
Professor Jiang!

20:00.990 --> 20:01.580
Professor Jiang!

20:01.580 --> 20:02.710
Mind your behavior!

20:02.710 --> 20:03.440
Please control yourself!

20:03.440 --> 20:04.030
Everyone, look!

20:04.030 --> 20:05.300
The police are beating me!

20:05.300 --> 20:07.470
Look! The police are beating me!

20:07.540 --> 20:07.910
Move.

20:07.940 --> 20:08.590
Move!

20:09.250 --> 20:09.730
Move!

20:17.640 --> 20:18.240
Hansheng.

20:22.470 --> 20:23.600
Professor Jiang...

20:25.030 --> 20:26.140
why did you do that?

20:26.190 --> 20:26.790
Chief Tan,

20:28.310 --> 20:29.370
Lai San's left hand

20:29.550 --> 20:30.810
has no strength at all.

20:31.600 --> 20:32.350
He alone

20:32.550 --> 20:33.470
couldn't possibly have

20:33.470 --> 20:35.800
carried out the murder and body disposal.

20:35.880 --> 20:38.310
I suspect there was a third person
at the scene.

20:38.310 --> 20:39.200
We need to

20:39.230 --> 20:41.090
interrogate his men separately.

20:43.770 --> 20:45.640
So that was your purpose just now?

20:48.780 --> 20:49.270
No.

20:50.140 --> 20:51.670
I really did want to hit him.

21:48.360 --> 21:49.310
Open up! Open up!

21:50.470 --> 21:52.270
We're from the Nancheng Branch.

22:09.710 --> 22:10.470
Chief Tan,

22:10.850 --> 22:11.880
we've arrested Lai San's men.

22:11.880 --> 22:13.900
Should we bring them directly
to your precinct?

22:13.900 --> 22:15.700
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

22:16.330 --> 22:17.270
I know the law too.

22:17.270 --> 22:17.860
I know.

22:18.250 --> 22:20.210
You can only detain me for 48 hours.

22:20.920 --> 22:22.800
When time's up and you've got no evidence,

22:22.800 --> 22:24.950
you'll have to respectfully send me home.

22:24.950 --> 22:25.550
Otherwise,

22:25.550 --> 22:28.810
I'll file a complaint against you
at the municipal bureau.

22:28.950 --> 22:29.800
Dream on.

22:30.290 --> 22:32.150
Setting Meng Ling's case aside for now—

22:32.150 --> 22:34.320
just for the charge of
organizing prostitution alone,

22:34.320 --> 22:35.320
you won't get out.

22:39.190 --> 22:40.000
No, no, no,

22:40.300 --> 22:41.500
my arm hurts too much.

22:41.720 --> 22:42.180
Listen,

22:42.250 --> 22:43.190
I need to go to the hospital.

22:43.190 --> 22:44.110
I really need medical attention!

22:44.110 --> 22:46.080
Your guy was way too rough!

22:46.080 --> 22:47.480
He could've crippled me!

22:47.600 --> 22:48.730
I'm going to sue him!

22:49.040 --> 22:49.770
Don't worry.

22:50.540 --> 22:51.930
The doctor is on his way.

22:52.240 --> 22:53.820
We'll have you thoroughly examined.

22:53.820 --> 22:54.310
Besides,

22:54.310 --> 22:56.030
we've checked your medical records

22:56.030 --> 22:57.970
in the City Central Hospital system.

22:57.970 --> 22:58.700
One year ago,

22:58.760 --> 22:59.760
you were in a fight

22:59.890 --> 23:01.220
and broke your left arm.

23:01.310 --> 23:03.780
After it healed,
though it didn't affect your daily life,

23:03.780 --> 23:04.610
your left hand

23:04.670 --> 23:06.220
couldn't lift heavy objects anymore.

23:06.220 --> 23:07.220
Isn't that right?

23:07.600 --> 23:08.460
Lai Zhengtian.

23:09.100 --> 23:10.100
Trying to fool us?

23:10.520 --> 23:11.780
It's not going to work.

23:13.360 --> 23:14.250
He Wu.

23:15.290 --> 23:16.010
Mr. He.

23:16.770 --> 23:17.850
Boss He!

23:18.270 --> 23:19.530
No, no, you flatter me.

23:19.750 --> 23:20.670
Just call me He Wu.

23:20.670 --> 23:22.190
Surname He, given name Wu.

23:23.760 --> 23:25.960
What's your relationship with Lai San?

23:26.190 --> 23:28.430
You mean... Lai Zhengtian, right?

23:28.810 --> 23:29.290
Yes.

23:29.870 --> 23:30.730
Lai Zhengtian.

23:31.520 --> 23:32.580
My distant cousin.

23:32.880 --> 23:33.880
A distant cousin.

23:34.030 --> 23:35.030
What stake

23:35.310 --> 23:36.970
does this cousin of yours hold

23:37.270 --> 23:39.000
in Hengyun Logistics Company?

23:39.390 --> 23:40.190
Five percent.

23:41.390 --> 23:42.720
What exactly does he do?

23:43.750 --> 23:45.470
What can he do?

23:46.630 --> 23:47.670
He's family.

23:48.130 --> 23:49.090
Lai San... oh no,

23:49.840 --> 23:50.710
Lai Zhengtian.

23:51.170 --> 23:53.060
He's idle all day,

23:53.130 --> 23:54.120
can't hold down a regular job,

23:54.120 --> 23:55.720
and can't do any proper work.

23:56.070 --> 23:58.250
Out of respect
for our family relationship,

23:58.250 --> 24:01.250
I just find an excuse
to give him some living expenses.

24:01.290 --> 24:02.270
Understandable.

24:02.270 --> 24:03.270
Understandable.

24:04.400 --> 24:06.130
What about his other business?

24:07.050 --> 24:08.680
He has other business?

24:10.150 --> 24:11.880
I really don't know about that.

24:12.380 --> 24:13.780
Well, Mr. Lai,

24:13.980 --> 24:15.170
for him, this sex trade

24:15.170 --> 24:17.030
isn't mainly about making money.

24:17.080 --> 24:18.950
It's mainly about having us girls

24:19.090 --> 24:20.330
please the guys

24:20.360 --> 24:21.750
and make the big shots happy.

24:21.750 --> 24:22.270
Get it?

24:23.190 --> 24:24.190
Be more specific.

24:24.480 --> 24:25.480
Please whom?

24:25.840 --> 24:27.170
I dare not tell you that.

24:27.400 --> 24:29.470
I'm already in enough trouble.

24:29.500 --> 24:30.680
I don't want to lose my life.

24:30.680 --> 24:32.960
You can forget about getting out of here.

24:33.430 --> 24:35.800
Just tell us how Meng Ling died.

24:35.820 --> 24:37.140
Save everyone's time!

24:38.920 --> 24:39.920
She was just a bitch.

24:39.920 --> 24:41.720
It wouldn't be a pity if she died.

24:41.820 --> 24:43.480
But I had nothing to do with it.

24:45.600 --> 24:46.230
Well,

24:46.310 --> 24:47.000
Mr. He,

24:47.830 --> 24:50.630
you can't pretend not to know
what's going on here.

24:51.330 --> 24:52.440
No, of course not.

24:52.780 --> 24:55.040
How could I still play dumb at this point?

24:56.570 --> 24:58.080
I was just sleeping at home that day.

24:58.080 --> 24:59.210
Didn't go anywhere.

24:59.380 --> 25:00.310
Who can prove it?

25:00.790 --> 25:01.850
My bed can prove it.

25:02.000 --> 25:03.260
Are you messing with us?

25:03.260 --> 25:03.930
Be honest!

25:05.080 --> 25:06.610
What could I possibly know?

25:06.640 --> 25:07.880
I'm just a nobody.

25:08.430 --> 25:09.490
You helped him open

25:09.840 --> 25:11.300
Phoenix Fire, didn't you?

25:11.410 --> 25:14.020
How could I have
opened Phoenix Fire for him?

25:14.880 --> 25:16.790
Phoenix Fire is
a legitimate establishment.

25:16.790 --> 25:18.750
We have a proper business license

25:18.770 --> 25:19.910
and an official organizational structure.

25:19.910 --> 25:20.470
We're...

25:20.670 --> 25:21.940
We're running a legitimate business.

25:21.940 --> 25:24.400
Whether it's legitimate or not,
we'll see later.

25:24.400 --> 25:25.260
First, tell me,

25:25.800 --> 25:28.040
who's really in charge of Phoenix Fire?

25:29.550 --> 25:31.880
Strictly speaking, Phoenix Fire is

25:32.890 --> 25:35.450
now fully managed by Jiang Cheng.

25:35.800 --> 25:36.330
It has...

25:36.520 --> 25:38.920
has nothing to do
with Lai Zhengtian at all.

25:41.150 --> 25:42.110
Lai Zhengtian.

25:42.980 --> 25:45.710
We're giving you a chance
by letting you confess.

25:45.760 --> 25:47.000
What chance?

25:48.150 --> 25:49.350
Do you have evidence?

25:50.040 --> 25:51.440
If you have evidence, I'll admit it.

25:51.440 --> 25:52.570
Do you have any?

26:04.000 --> 26:05.130
I'll get some sleep.

26:14.680 --> 26:15.680
If I tell you...

26:17.080 --> 26:18.480
can you take down Lai San?

26:21.840 --> 26:23.630
As long as the evidence is solid,

26:23.630 --> 26:25.310
we won't let any criminal

26:25.330 --> 26:26.370
escape justice.

26:27.030 --> 26:28.160
Well, by that logic,

26:29.910 --> 26:32.440
there wouldn't be any bad people
in the world.

26:33.870 --> 26:34.600
That's true.

26:35.270 --> 26:36.670
Lai San isn't even human.

26:37.410 --> 26:38.780
He's just a dog.

26:39.310 --> 26:41.030
A filthy dog, a mad dog!

26:42.390 --> 26:43.390
Meng Ling is dead.

26:44.110 --> 26:45.440
He must have killed her.

26:45.750 --> 26:46.880
Why are you so sure?

26:47.620 --> 26:49.800
Meng Ling was from a village in Honglian

26:49.800 --> 26:51.600
and didn't have much schooling.

26:51.790 --> 26:53.400
Her pride was her undoing.

26:54.780 --> 26:56.240
It was also her bad luck...

26:58.360 --> 27:00.220
to meet Lai San, that cunning fox.

27:00.720 --> 27:03.450
Even nine lives
wouldn't be enough for his games.

27:03.650 --> 27:05.780
Lai San gave her some brand-name bags.

27:05.960 --> 27:07.620
They were all fake, actually.

27:08.670 --> 27:09.870
She got carried away.

27:10.800 --> 27:12.450
Thought she'd met someone
who could help her

27:12.450 --> 27:14.110
and that she could make it big.

27:14.950 --> 27:16.080
What happened next?

27:17.790 --> 27:19.420
After Lai San won her over...

27:22.180 --> 27:24.090
that very night, he brought several men,

27:24.090 --> 27:25.490
and they gang-raped her.

27:26.750 --> 27:29.150
How could a young girl like her
handle that?

27:29.180 --> 27:30.710
Lai San was truly ruthless—

27:31.180 --> 27:32.950
he forced her to prostitute herself

27:32.950 --> 27:35.010
and beat her severely every few days.

27:35.410 --> 27:36.410
And then later...

27:39.010 --> 27:40.140
About two years ago,

27:41.610 --> 27:42.400
Boss He—

27:43.040 --> 27:44.080
Lai San's cousin,

27:44.320 --> 27:44.910
He Wu—

27:45.400 --> 27:46.430
had a man

27:47.190 --> 27:48.800
working for him named Cheng.

27:49.840 --> 27:51.640
This guy Cheng was very capable.

27:52.120 --> 27:53.400
Boss He entrusted him with

27:53.400 --> 27:55.130
most of his business dealings.

27:55.440 --> 27:56.700
What kind of business?

28:01.000 --> 28:02.130
Logistics, I think.

28:03.340 --> 28:05.400
I don't really understand it either.

28:05.800 --> 28:06.360
Go on.

28:07.360 --> 28:09.680
Lai San, in order to
curry favor with Cheng,

28:09.680 --> 28:11.090
sent Meng Ling to him.

28:12.730 --> 28:13.860
Meng Ling told me...

28:15.950 --> 28:17.810
Cheng was a different kind of man.

28:18.490 --> 28:19.420
He treasured her

28:20.400 --> 28:22.270
and didn't treat her like a prostitute.

28:22.270 --> 28:24.870
Cheng even encouraged her
to go back to school,

28:25.840 --> 28:26.600
telling her

28:27.510 --> 28:29.770
that as long as one has determination...

28:30.750 --> 28:32.030
it's never too late.

28:32.800 --> 28:34.330
Meng Ling remembered that.

28:35.530 --> 28:37.900
She wrote it on her wall
and read it every day.

28:37.900 --> 28:40.300
What does that have to do
with Lai Zhengtian?

28:40.300 --> 28:41.690
Lai San sent Meng Ling

28:42.920 --> 28:44.050
to kiss up to Cheng,

28:45.310 --> 28:46.120
but Cheng

28:46.120 --> 28:47.780
didn't buy into his act at all.

28:48.600 --> 28:49.780
Once, when Lai San messed up

28:49.780 --> 28:51.920
a business deal for the logistics company,

28:51.920 --> 28:53.160
Cheng slapped him across the face

28:53.160 --> 28:54.360
in front of everyone.

28:54.800 --> 28:57.190
If Boss He hadn't stepped in at that time,

28:57.750 --> 28:59.330
those two would have fought,

28:59.330 --> 29:01.460
and one of them would surely have died.

29:01.790 --> 29:02.930
But not long after,

29:03.630 --> 29:06.030
Boss He transferred Cheng to another city,

29:06.510 --> 29:07.860
and he never came back.

29:09.240 --> 29:10.900
He could just leave like that,

29:12.390 --> 29:13.720
but Meng Ling couldn't.

29:17.620 --> 29:20.270
Lai San, having been humiliated,

29:22.270 --> 29:23.800
took it all out on Meng Ling.

29:26.160 --> 29:26.990
I swear,

29:28.480 --> 29:29.740
if Meng Ling is dead...

29:31.830 --> 29:33.690
Lai San is definitely the killer.

29:34.730 --> 29:37.460
What's the full name of this Cheng
you mentioned?

29:39.340 --> 29:40.100
Jiang Cheng.

29:50.050 --> 29:53.030
[Jiang Cheng]

29:58.710 --> 29:59.640
Jiang Hansheng.

30:00.990 --> 30:02.120
Don't do that again.

30:02.940 --> 30:04.140
It's very dangerous.

30:20.490 --> 30:22.290
When did you start following me?

30:25.810 --> 30:27.610
That man was Jiang Cheng, right?

30:32.230 --> 30:33.130
I don't mind.

30:37.370 --> 30:39.170
There's nothing to worry about.

30:40.380 --> 30:41.910
We just ran into each other,

30:41.990 --> 30:43.790
and then

30:43.840 --> 30:45.770
some unpleasant things happened.

30:46.640 --> 30:48.370
You don't need to explain to me.

30:54.790 --> 30:55.320
Zhou Jin.

30:56.990 --> 30:58.230
Stay here tonight,

30:58.680 --> 30:59.360
okay?

31:05.410 --> 31:08.140
I still have some clothes
I haven't brought over—

31:08.400 --> 31:09.880
pajamas and such...

31:09.880 --> 31:10.550
Wear mine.

31:16.680 --> 31:17.600
I need you.

31:31.620 --> 31:34.700
♪ Across the mountain ♪

31:35.060 --> 31:38.120
♪ A lonely boat waits ♪

31:38.330 --> 31:41.280
♪ Is it there ♪

31:41.810 --> 31:44.780
♪ For you to come ashore? ♪

31:45.270 --> 31:48.080
♪ Your questions ♪

31:48.680 --> 31:51.530
♪ I dare not ask ♪

31:52.000 --> 31:54.790
♪ If I did, I fear ♪

31:55.440 --> 31:58.320
♪ I'd throw caution to the wind for you ♪

31:58.830 --> 32:01.840
♪ The night is dark ♪

32:02.230 --> 32:05.270
♪ Dawn or dusk ♪

32:05.640 --> 32:09.180
♪ I don't want past memories ♪

32:09.380 --> 32:11.850
♪ To run wild again ♪

32:12.300 --> 32:15.320
♪ It was you who pushed open ♪

32:15.340 --> 32:17.770
♪ The door to my heart ♪

32:18.730 --> 32:22.020
♪ And now ♪

32:22.580 --> 32:25.710
♪ We're both more serious than before ♪

32:26.030 --> 32:28.600
♪ You've become ♪

32:28.620 --> 32:31.770
♪ My guiding star ♪

32:32.250 --> 32:37.770
♪ I don't want to dwell on ♪

32:39.010 --> 32:42.270
♪ The endless ticking of time ♪

32:42.300 --> 32:45.520
♪ My longing for you runs deep ♪

32:45.820 --> 32:48.770
♪ In that wavering moment ♪

32:49.760 --> 32:55.610
♪ Every door of my heart opens wide ♪

33:08.570 --> 33:09.230
Good night.

33:51.180 --> 33:51.960
What...

33:52.470 --> 33:54.120
book were you just reading?

33:56.050 --> 33:57.250
The Lord of the Rings.

33:58.900 --> 33:59.990
I hear the movies

34:01.190 --> 34:02.720
based on it are really good.

34:07.940 --> 34:08.540
Zhou Jin?

34:10.010 --> 34:11.010
Let's go to sleep.

34:29.290 --> 34:29.820
Zhou Jin?

34:54.790 --> 34:55.520
Are you okay?

34:55.830 --> 34:56.989
I'm fine. You?

34:59.600 --> 35:00.730
We're both wounded.

35:12.820 --> 35:13.750
Jiang Hansheng.

35:18.730 --> 35:19.460
You seem...

35:19.850 --> 35:20.850
different today.

35:23.410 --> 35:24.080
Really?

35:34.490 --> 35:35.200
Zhou Jin.

35:37.780 --> 35:39.240
Thank you for marrying me.

35:44.620 --> 35:46.280
Your heart is beating so fast.

35:49.920 --> 35:50.440
No way.

35:51.750 --> 35:53.480
I have a low resting heart rate.

35:57.330 --> 35:58.330
You...

36:00.750 --> 36:01.810
smell really nice.

36:04.170 --> 36:04.810
Do I?

36:19.100 --> 36:20.540
Do I smell nicer than him?

37:05.430 --> 37:06.070
Zhou Jin.

37:07.360 --> 37:08.160
You're awake.

37:09.100 --> 37:10.160
What are you doing?

37:11.790 --> 37:13.920
I'm writing a self-criticism report.

37:16.160 --> 37:17.620
Taking medicine so early?

37:17.910 --> 37:18.440
It hurts.

37:19.070 --> 37:19.950
Are those

37:20.110 --> 37:21.070
painkillers?

37:26.590 --> 37:27.900
Then don't take them on an empty stomach.

37:27.900 --> 37:28.830
Have some bread.

37:31.410 --> 37:32.610
My ribs hurt a bit too.

37:36.170 --> 37:37.300
You don't need this.

37:40.310 --> 37:40.970
Wait for me.

37:58.200 --> 37:59.200
You can take this.

38:05.680 --> 38:07.880
You didn't even ask what medicine it is.

38:09.200 --> 38:10.800
You wouldn't harm me anyway.

38:14.300 --> 38:15.500
Finally finished it.

38:17.600 --> 38:18.130
Alright,

38:18.160 --> 38:19.420
I need to go to work now.

38:20.460 --> 38:21.590
Is something wrong?

38:21.660 --> 38:23.660
You're not uncomfortable, are you?

38:23.870 --> 38:26.330
How's the case investigation progressing?

38:29.200 --> 38:30.560
We've already confirmed with the coroner

38:30.560 --> 38:32.830
that there are indeed no drag marks
on Meng Ling's body.

38:32.830 --> 38:34.040
Just as you said that day,

38:34.040 --> 38:35.710
if Lai San really committed the crime,

38:35.710 --> 38:36.920
he must have had an accomplice

38:36.920 --> 38:38.420
to help dispose of the body.

38:38.420 --> 38:39.420
The crime scene is

38:39.510 --> 38:41.390
quite far from downtown,

38:41.470 --> 38:43.080
so they must have used a vehicle.

38:43.080 --> 38:44.630
So the first thing we need to check

38:44.630 --> 38:45.580
is all the vehicles

38:45.580 --> 38:46.980
under Lai San's control.

38:47.440 --> 38:48.670
As for Lai San himself,

38:48.670 --> 38:50.040
we've already interrogated him once.

38:50.040 --> 38:51.420
He lives up to his reputation—

38:51.420 --> 38:52.750
he's truly a scoundrel.

38:53.420 --> 38:55.830
Lai San has strong psychological defenses.

38:55.830 --> 38:57.560
Don't waste time trying to
get him to confess.

38:57.560 --> 38:58.310
I suggest

38:58.660 --> 39:00.560
investigating his personal relationships—

39:00.560 --> 39:02.530
who he's close to
and who he has conflicts with.

39:02.530 --> 39:03.660
Find his weak spots.

39:05.120 --> 39:06.580
I'm going to Phoenix Fire.

39:10.210 --> 39:10.740
Zhou Jin.

39:13.870 --> 39:14.930
Going there again?

39:15.310 --> 39:16.370
Wanna come with me?

39:17.780 --> 39:18.510
I have class.

39:19.480 --> 39:20.540
Then I'll go ahead.

39:23.170 --> 39:24.170
Professor Jiang,

39:24.310 --> 39:26.170
anything else you need to tell me?

39:29.020 --> 39:29.500
No.

39:30.450 --> 39:31.510
I'll be going then.

39:50.460 --> 39:51.460
Professor Jiang,

39:51.630 --> 39:52.960
how is your injury?

39:53.520 --> 39:54.120
Chief Tan,

39:54.800 --> 39:56.180
are most of Lai Zhengtian's connections

39:56.180 --> 39:57.510
in Phoenix Fire?

39:57.720 --> 39:58.050
Yes.

39:58.570 --> 39:59.370
What's wrong?

40:00.620 --> 40:03.220
Zhou Jin's already gone
to do the questioning.

40:03.750 --> 40:04.880
We're on our way too.

40:05.880 --> 40:06.680
You all going?

40:06.790 --> 40:07.310
What?

40:08.060 --> 40:09.190
Are you free to come?

40:10.880 --> 40:12.390
I still have class this morning.

40:12.390 --> 40:13.860
Zhou Jin is already on her way.

40:13.860 --> 40:15.460
I just wanted to let you know.

40:15.980 --> 40:16.480
Okay.

40:17.110 --> 40:19.300
I'll contact you if anything comes up.

40:52.830 --> 40:53.230
Cheng!

40:53.310 --> 40:53.710
Cheng!

40:53.800 --> 40:54.200
Cheng!

40:54.440 --> 40:54.840
Cheng!

40:54.980 --> 40:55.560
Cheng!

40:55.590 --> 40:56.560
Cheng!

40:56.580 --> 40:57.200
Cheng!

41:05.230 --> 41:06.230
Officers,

41:06.560 --> 41:08.520
why don't you take these people back
for questioning?

41:08.520 --> 41:09.260
Can you do that?

41:09.260 --> 41:10.130
Your cars are all parked at the entrance.

41:10.130 --> 41:11.930
How am I supposed to do business?

41:13.590 --> 41:15.190
This is standard procedure.

41:15.310 --> 41:17.110
Please cooperate with our work.

41:17.620 --> 41:18.280
Cooperate.

41:18.560 --> 41:19.220
Cooperate.

41:19.880 --> 41:21.500
Cooperate properly. You hear that?

41:21.500 --> 41:22.850
-Got it!
-Got it!

41:24.230 --> 41:24.750
Cheng.

41:25.400 --> 41:26.080
Chief Tan.

41:26.790 --> 41:28.790
Gather everyone
who's familiar with Lai Zhengtian

41:28.790 --> 41:30.190
and bring them together.

41:30.350 --> 41:31.550
Take them back first.

41:31.640 --> 41:32.000
Yes.

41:32.030 --> 41:32.600
Yes.

41:33.040 --> 41:34.970
Take all relevant personnel away!

41:39.930 --> 41:42.160
The Captain of the Criminal Investigation Brigade
leading the team himself.

41:42.160 --> 41:44.980
Looks like someone
committed quite a serious crime.

41:44.980 --> 41:45.980
What's your name?

41:48.350 --> 41:49.080
Jiang Cheng.

41:51.680 --> 41:52.610
Nice to meet you.

41:57.140 --> 41:58.400
Did you know Meng Ling?

41:59.000 --> 41:59.600
Yes, I did.

41:59.990 --> 42:01.310
What was your relationship?

42:01.310 --> 42:02.960
We didn't have any relationship.

42:02.960 --> 42:04.420
According to what we know,

42:04.500 --> 42:05.730
you dated her.

42:07.160 --> 42:08.090
Were you lovers?

42:08.480 --> 42:09.750
Well, that depends on how your police

42:09.750 --> 42:11.390
define "lovers."

42:11.680 --> 42:14.230
If sleeping together a few times counts,

42:14.710 --> 42:16.710
then I'd have too many girlfriends.

42:17.440 --> 42:18.790
I see, I see.

42:20.250 --> 42:23.210
Just tell me yes or no.

42:28.090 --> 42:28.690
Chief Tan.

42:30.920 --> 42:31.780
No, we weren't.

42:32.440 --> 42:33.570
I have a girlfriend,

42:33.920 --> 42:35.080
and we're engaged.

42:36.510 --> 42:38.180
Since you knew Meng Ling...

42:42.380 --> 42:44.180
Did she ever mention in private

42:44.570 --> 42:45.900
whether she had grudges

42:46.390 --> 42:47.720
against Lai Zhengtian?

42:47.960 --> 42:48.560
No.

42:49.520 --> 42:50.580
What about Lai San?

42:51.000 --> 42:52.000
Did you notice...

42:53.350 --> 42:54.750
anyone threatening him?

42:57.120 --> 42:58.750
Whether Meng Ling
and Lai San had any conflicts,

42:58.750 --> 43:00.010
I honestly don't know.

43:00.680 --> 43:01.980
But if you're asking who in this place

43:01.980 --> 43:03.710
has the biggest grudge against Lai San,

43:03.710 --> 43:04.520
that would definitely be me.
